

# Employee Tracker App

Employee Tracker is a React Native application that allows employees to track their location and perform location tracking. The app utilizes the React Native Foreground Service for continuous location tracking.

## Features

- Signup using Email and Password
- Start and stop location tracking.
- Display real-time latitude and longitude using sliders.
- Perform check-ins with recorded location.
- regular Email notification of location
- Get Time to Time notification of latitude
- Location checkin history
- Logout functionality.

## Getting Started

To get started with the app, follow these steps:

### Prerequisites

- Node.js installed on your machine
- React native cli version > 72

### Installation

1. Clone the repository:

   git clone https://github.com/alok-56/Employe-App.git

open the terminal and use below command

2. npm install

3. npm start 

4. choose emultor

### Server Installation in local

1. clone the repository:

   git clone https://github.com/alok-56/Employe-App.git

open the terminal and use below command

2. npm Install

3. node index.js


NOTE : I HAVE DEPLOYED THE SERVER SO API  WILL RUN WITHOUT RUNNING SERVER IN LOCAL SYSTEM







 

